{"tid":473953,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實歐洲M記飲品都係冇膠袋。。","createTime":"2017-11-19T16:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T18:43:32.000Z","uid":89595,"like":570,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"759f8a401d48d6b9fd9b020644813a9a12237bf4","tid":473953,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"不過佢地有相應嘅措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/004630_07e4b992394efcc94ff83b82078684cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F004630_07e4b992394efcc94ff83b82078684cf.jpg&h=cbafe2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實香港可唔可以參考下咁樣？<br />\n又企理又環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而唔係就咁cut咗個膠袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa3351f692e02c655454b7ad7a6276868cc30e4","tid":473953,"uid":57962,"like":465,"dislike":3,"score":462,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:18:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0469c22a83a4e9cc7bdf0c9a1cd268685a56260a","tid":473953,"uid":46752,"like":19,"dislike":11,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"點用架"},{"pid":"6cf4be89566ac6b4caf884a772aa3b9cb59330a1","tid":473953,"uid":58140,"like":138,"dislike":3,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"環保紙袋代替膠袋係好<br />\n係香港本身環保意識低 就算好似你咁<br />\n到最後都係DOM落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8875323888cf6e8f3cab5e68940488cf4710170","tid":473953,"uid":89595,"like":88,"dislike":6,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地從用家角度出發<br />\n香港？<br />\n問佢攞多張紙巾好似殺左佢老豆老母咁</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間野你開架咩 咁緊張真係博最佳員工獎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420a003b57ee20a256a1ee88f0623ec479d35ea7","tid":473953,"uid":106027,"like":31,"dislike":10,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"買一個餐要你一隻手拎紙袋 另一隻手拎凍飲 門都開唔到喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有次問佢拎 佢仲話見我兩手空空 覺得我唔需要 畀我屌兩聲先肯死死氣畀我<br />\n<br />\n不過而家樓下果間畀人問得多 會自動入膠袋"},{"pid":"5ea544faa4ce48d1fe0fe6b1a459eb6b115659a4","tid":473953,"uid":89595,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環保紙袋代替膠袋係好<br />\n係香港本身環保意識低 就算好似你咁<br />\n到最後都係DOM落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢句真 喺呢到你唔分類比你發現好似都罰得幾重下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3f21ab947d1a3dc85bf0d3c56f6bb5c38a200b","tid":473953,"uid":131980,"like":503,"dislike":3,"score":500,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:34:49.000Z","msg":"我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認"},{"pid":"3389f15b99a795eb8a52fe558923aae289551e07","tid":473953,"uid":35730,"like":202,"dislike":3,"score":199,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認</blockquote><br />\n如果全部都好似你咁就正"},{"pid":"db6a54ec95481072fc83c73991ee8bb37bc0d959","tid":473953,"uid":59632,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得佢個外賣袋幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f4c45db8b44a80d46161420a52c74cc2ffb3ce","tid":473953,"uid":89595,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>環保紙袋代替膠袋係好<br />\n係香港本身環保意識低 就算好似你咁<br />\n到最後都係DOM落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢句真 喺呢到你唔分類比你發現好似都罰得幾重下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而喺香港會喺屋企分類嘅人應該真係唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5982a4ec0bdf664e9c7e3647f1830773d4bf852d","tid":473953,"uid":89595,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而覺得佢個外賣袋幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有個手抽係幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fc4aeb9b2ce968ca4c481f881244274b1f610b","tid":473953,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:38:39.000Z","msg":"拎到隻手濕晒"},{"pid":"22c721c561a2650afde59efbbff766271b32fd1e","tid":473953,"uid":10788,"like":343,"dislike":5,"score":338,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:39:37.000Z","msg":"我之前是在麥當勞打工的，而我產薯條的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次產的薯條就是姬芭一大包。小薯產成大薯，中薯產成巨薯。大薯買一送一，跟把整個薯條站的薯條全送給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月薯條虧損二十六箱，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"c5fd7386b8a30e69112cc91385bf97bfc4fa9bcd","tid":473953,"uid":143582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而覺得佢個外賣袋幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主咪就係講緊成set囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有手抽位既紙袋+個stand"},{"pid":"ca653add3622c8bdbaa4c605d4f23436f833c6f4","tid":473953,"uid":74380,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認</blockquote><br />\n如果全部都好似你咁就正</blockquote><br />\n小心比啲垃圾經理見到屌鳩你"},{"pid":"e65b8d303d60a6f116bf1a9772208a5509fc735e","tid":473953,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":70,"score":-69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前是在麥當勞打工的，而我產薯條的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次產的薯條就是姬芭一大包。小薯產成大薯，中薯產成巨薯。大薯買一送一，跟把整個薯條站的薯條全送給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月薯條虧損二十六箱，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。</blockquote><br />\n離題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ece7f5f99370fd19ba2ff7d57a955885a56be2","tid":473953,"uid":9284,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:44:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地從用家角度出發<br />\n香港？<br />\n問佢攞多張紙巾好似殺左佢老豆老母咁</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間野你開架咩 咁緊張真係博最佳員工獎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 好戇鳩 唔明做咩要幫佢慳<br />\n讀書時做m記成日入勁多薯條比人"},{"pid":"f5e98fc4313b95e31620282116dc4ba39f308546","tid":473953,"uid":42364,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"一味識講環保<br />\n但又冇足夠配套<br />\n我屋企啲廢物分撚哂類<br />\n屌你老母一句個箱有其他垃圾就掉撚哂去堆填區<br />\n一句有其他樽未撚洗乾淨又掉去堆填區<br />\n係咪咁低技術連揀走其他野都做唔到<br />\n 屌你老母諗到我分左類啲野都係去堆填區<br />\n我分黎做乜春？"},{"pid":"c8be284255ec6b8e82a8dc03c551e9fed0dadc6b","tid":473953,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地從用家角度出發<br />\n香港？<br />\n問佢攞多張紙巾好似殺左佢老豆老母咁</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間野你開架咩 咁緊張真係博最佳員工獎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 好戇鳩 唔明做咩要幫佢慳<br />\n讀書時做m記成日入勁多薯條比人</blockquote><br />\n雪糕一定勁多圈突晒出黎  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d171a00239137eef30096a21ed883df76975f40","tid":473953,"uid":17232,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認</blockquote><br />\n我之前是在麥當勞打工的，而我產薯條的原則是：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「幹你娘塞爆」</span></span><br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次產的薯條就是雞巴一大包。小薯產成大薯，中薯產成巨薯。大薯買一送一，跟把整個薯條站的薯條全送給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月薯條虧損二十六箱，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"80dbe6d0f56dad1e34614e4afe3f44fc0b82a561","tid":473953,"uid":9284,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認</blockquote><br />\n如果全部都好似你咁就正</blockquote><br />\n小心比啲垃圾經理見到屌鳩你</blockquote><br />\n屌完第2日全部外賣客我送多盒薯條<br />\n最多咪走人呢d西工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997ee7181a14c81730eb27f79325b3459177e178","tid":473953,"uid":58393,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:01:31.000Z","msg":"做員工撚會同你慳咩<br />\n最多都係啲呀嬸以為慳得多有人工加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係唔預設比飲品袋真係好反智<br />\n首先公司出發點唔係慳<br />\n而係比埋綠色狗咬住唔放<br />\n我夠膽講100個客人99個都要飲品袋<br />\n如果有綠色狗係度既話 我屌你老母<br />\n用下你個豬腦啦<br />\n你扑野係咪唔撚戴套？定會洗完再用？<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢員工"},{"pid":"ac2164b8c76c26cf4dd3f3460bffd5a474ec52a4","tid":473953,"uid":104748,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:05:03.000Z","msg":"同香港人講環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc7e8a23963625a1e724f95ba8b113bb201c376","tid":473953,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>環保紙袋代替膠袋係好<br />\n係香港本身環保意識低 就算好似你咁<br />\n到最後都係DOM落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢句真 喺呢到你唔分類比你發現好似都罰得幾重下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而喺香港會喺屋企分類嘅人應該真係唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好少地方有回收箱就真"},{"pid":"4e978aca9e4ade4348ed85185e9a2ede8b6488b8","tid":473953,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:26:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2173418383b98d5e73569f9016d6d71ddef192e","tid":473953,"uid":50328,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:32:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1adae4bcca108c40ed9beebb9811aed27517e8cc","tid":473953,"uid":8850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T22:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>環保紙袋代替膠袋係好<br />\n係香港本身環保意識低 就算好似你咁<br />\n到最後都係DOM落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢句真 喺呢到你唔分類比你發現好似都罰得幾重下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但聽聞而家係請左人係堆填區分類垃圾種類：膠還膠。紙還紙。金屬還金屬。"},{"pid":"15bc1b7bc77c0ff3d58d79741323c9c5d19328fa","tid":473953,"uid":72946,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T23:46:28.000Z","msg":"張檯有咁窄得咁窄，張凳有咁迫得咁迫，咪等啲友坐得咁舒服，食完嗱嗱聲好走；支飲管有咁粗得咁粗，冰有咁大舊放咁大舊，杯汽水咪啅一聲飲完買過第二杯囉。"},{"pid":"9be1900b833c94adfab1e7f470ca7dbca2f24940","tid":473953,"uid":94102,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前是在麥當勞打工的，而我產薯條的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次產的薯條就是姬芭一大包。小薯產成大薯，中薯產成巨薯。大薯買一送一，跟把整個薯條站的薯條全送給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月薯條虧損二十六箱，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。</blockquote><br />\n牛 B"},{"pid":"cd5decd9773b103f0cc5adb09b351e03a9d4fe36","tid":473953,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認</blockquote><br />\n如果全部都好似你咁就正</blockquote><br />\n小心比啲垃圾經理見到屌鳩你</blockquote><br />\n屌完第2日全部外賣客我送多盒薯條<br />\n最多咪走人呢d西工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fd93556f93c45a6c8960f5371753bae60dd167","tid":473953,"uid":37005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:57:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認</blockquote><br />\n如果全部都好似你咁就正</blockquote><br />\n小心比啲垃圾經理見到屌鳩你</blockquote><br />\n屌完第2日全部外賣客我送多盒薯條<br />\n最多咪走人呢d西工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個員工都好似巴打咁就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過買雪糕裡面空氣嚟 好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2b15cc964ad20828bdea8ff509137d851a5454","tid":473953,"uid":139843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:15:29.000Z","msg":"記得個時返KFC pt<br />\n開始徵收膠袋錢<br />\n堂食完食唔哂要收返5毫子攞膠袋<br />\n香港人直接無端端收5毫子又要開機咁on99<br />\n淨係收個啲大陸閪，賓賓，南亞狗<br />\n鬼叫你哋冇禮貌又麻撚煩煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e276baecef25cb638b16e3a902bc6925fa2fd38c","tid":473953,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得個時返KFC pt<br />\n開始徵收膠袋錢<br />\n堂食完食唔哂要收返5毫子攞膠袋<br />\n香港人直接無端端收5毫子又要開機咁on99<br />\n淨係收個啲大陸閪，賓賓，南亞狗<br />\n鬼叫你哋冇禮貌又麻撚煩煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但唔收唔係犯法咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63686921bb2d40ce8f32a0956b1d8a7a0b61cc60","tid":473953,"uid":64609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認</blockquote><br />\n如果全部都好似你咁就正</blockquote><br />\n小心比啲垃圾經理見到屌鳩你</blockquote><br />\n屌完第2日全部外賣客我送多盒薯條<br />\n最多咪走人呢d西工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個員工都好似巴打咁就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過買雪糕裡面空氣嚟 好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D咁既工隨時走都得啦洗乜怕佢屌"},{"pid":"a107ff28cc6eaff96e02f4c467320c51e77f90f5","tid":473953,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:25:08.000Z","msg":"香港同你講成本，紙袋工序成本可以係4-5倍"},{"pid":"04234cd9585fb2de4e1591464709969e5d164f89","tid":473953,"uid":79995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6617e0fe9cb902eb99404a0ea6a13cecfed2ad72","tid":473953,"uid":93987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認</blockquote><br />\n我都係，成日啲同事都問我做咩杯雪糕咁大杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca479bf314b3f83248eb4d7be1e5f5907dce8d24","tid":473953,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"大家討論重點講遠咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3063f6b451273f6545c6bcfaafc31c0ad52447ce","tid":473953,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港同你講成本，紙袋工序成本可以係4-5倍</blockquote><br />\n工序我諗都明<br />\n紙袋差價差幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47395909fbc73ddc002e0df6fca3798dfa340d94","tid":473953,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>環保紙袋代替膠袋係好<br />\n係香港本身環保意識低 就算好似你咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">到最後都係DOM落垃圾桶</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n</blockquote><br />\nOn9 你比較下2者分解速度同去到堆田區對環境有咩影響先好講啦 而家擺明係唔用膠好過用膠<br />\n<br />\n慢慢話我左膠啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d058c1ea2b79033ce038d778f1fc48972ab1539e","tid":473953,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我先唔同間垃圾店慳<br />\n雪糕大大杯,正常兩圈半,我比夠四圈,杯裝就實芯.<br />\n薯條中SIZE裝到變大SIZE<br />\n野飲少冰我比三粒<br />\n餐紙我大大疊比o的客<br />\n茄汁5-6包<br />\n<br />\n總之有得令間鋪蝕錢我都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前做過,勿相認</blockquote><br />\n我之前係係麥當勞打工的，而我產薯條既原則係：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「屌那媽塞爆」</span></span><br />\n冇錯，就係屌那媽塞爆，阿叔理撚得咩公司虧損乜鳩，每次產薯條就係黑鮑咁大包。小薯產到變大薯，中薯產到變巨薯。大薯買一送一，同將成個薯條站啲薯條送哂比你冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n我仲記得，我嗰個月返左25日，經理過黎問我，呢個月薯條虧損二十六箱，你有冇咩頭緒？<br />\n<br />\n我撚知咩。</blockquote><br />\n廣東話版</blockquote><br />\n都係自己母語最有親切感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3b6395a3703138558b97eabb7221de41b54f97","tid":473953,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>環保紙袋代替膠袋係好<br />\n係香港本身環保意識低 就算好似你咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">到最後都係DOM落垃圾桶</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n</blockquote><br />\nOn9 你比較下2者分解速度同去到堆田區對環境有咩影響先好講啦 而家擺明係唔用膠好過用膠<br />\n<br />\n慢慢話我左膠啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我淨係知而家好唔方便 分唔分解到關我咩事呀"},{"pid":"382a08d44d28b3c2430edf6b7fcf9056d93